  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees.",
    "Slice the baguette into 1 inch thick slices.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together minced garlic and salt.",
    "Brush each slice of bread with olive oil and sprinkle with garlic salt mixture.",
    "Place the slices on a baking sheet and bake for 10 minutes or until crispy.",
    "Remove from oven and sprinkle with grana padano cheese and parsley.",
    "Return to oven and bake for an additional 2 minutes or until cheese is melted.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for a few minutes.",
    "Serve in a molcajete and enjoy."
